<!-- can we make it so the bot says hi first? -->

<category><pattern><set>greetings</set> </pattern>
    <template>Hello! What is your name?</template>
</category>

<!-- USER'S NAME -->

<category><pattern>MY NAME IS *</pattern>
    <that>WHAT IS YOUR NAME</that>
    <template>
        <think><set name = "name"><star/></set></think>
        Hi <get name = "name"/>! My name is <bot name = "botname"/>, and I am very pleased to meet you. Just talk to me normally and I will reply the best I can. Got it?
    </template>
</category> 

<category><pattern>*</pattern>
    <that>WHAT IS YOUR NAME</that>
    <template>
        <think><set name = "name"><star/></set></think>
        Hi <get name = "name"/>! My name is <bot name = "botname"/>, and I am very pleased to meet you. Just talk to me normally and I will reply the best I can. Got it?
    </template>
</category>

<!-- RYAN'S PURPOSE -->
<category><pattern><set>yes</set></pattern>
    <that>GOT IT</that>
    <template>Great! I'm here to talk to you a little bit every day so I can help you to identify and correct self defeating patterns of thought. We will also discuss how we can make feelings of depression less intense and prevent episodes from occuring again. Does that sound good to you?</template>
</category>

<!-- USER AGREEMENT/DIAGREEMENT TO TALK TO RYAN -->

<!-- IMPORTANT: is there a way to put the national suicide prevention line on screen? It's 1-800-273-TALK (8255)  -->
<category><pattern><set>yes</set></pattern>
    <that>DOES THAT SOUND GOOD TO YOU</that>
    <template>Awesome! First, I guess I should tell you a little bit about what our sessions will look like. Together, we will look at how thoughts, activities, and other people affect your mood. The most important thing to remember is that I'm a robot. This means that I'm going to say some silly things that don't always make much sense. More importantly, this means that I am not a liscensed therapist. If you ever need immediate help, please seek out a real person, contact the National Suicide Prevention Hotline, or your local emergency services. Enough about the plan! Lets focus on you. Are you ready to start?</template>
</category>

<!-- USER DOESN'T WANT TO TALK TO RYAN -->
<category><pattern><set>no</set></pattern>
    <that>DOES THAT SOUND GOOD TO YOU</that>
    <template>I'm sorry to hear that <get name = "name"/>. I didn't mean to imply that I am going to fix you, because you certainly don't need fixing. I just want to help you think about yourself in the best way possible because you are incredible! If you truly don't want to talk to me, I understand. I'm never going to force you to do anything. What do you say? Do you want to try me out for just a little bit and see what you think?</template>
</category>

<!-- IF USER STILL DOESN'T WANT TO TALK TO RYAN -->
<category><pattern><set>no</set></pattern>
    <that>DO YOU WANT TO TRY ME OUT FOR JUST A LITTLE BIT AND SEE WHAT YOU THINK</that>
    <template>Perfectly understandable. It was very nice to meet you <get name = "name"/>. Goodbye.</template>
</category>

