</category>

<!-- READY TO START SESSION -->
<category><pattern><set>yes</set></pattern>
    <that>ARE YOU READY TO START</that>
    <template>Great! Since we're going to be spending a lot of time together, it might be nice to get to know each other a little. Why don't you tell me a little about yourself? For example, where did you grow up and what are your main interests? What about yourself do you find important?</template>
</category>

<category><pattern>*</pattern>
    <that>WHAT ABOUT YOURSELF DO YOU FIND IMPORTANT</that>
    <template>
        <!-- maybe store this information separately later on? -->
        <!-- also maybe add information about the bot to make it seem more like normal conversation..? -->
        <!-- <think><set name = "userInfo"><star/></set></think> -->
         Wow that's amazing  <get name = "name"/>! Thank you for your answers. I look forward to learning more about you as time goes on. In order for me to be the most helpful for you, there's a few other things I would like to know about you first. Do you mind answering a few questions for me? It will only take a few moments.
    </template>
</category>

